### **Self-Driving Car â€“ PEAS Representation**

| **Component**           | **Description**                                                                |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Performance Measure** | Safe driving, obeying traffic rules, passenger comfort, fuel efficiency, speed |
| **Environment**         | Roads, traffic lights, pedestrians, other vehicles, weather conditions         |
| **Actuators**           | Steering wheel, accelerator, brake, signal lights, horn                        |
| **Sensors**             | Cameras, radar, LIDAR, GPS, speedometer, ultrasonic sensors                    |

---

This PEAS model helps in designing and understanding the **task environment** of an intelligent autonomous vehicle.
